---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Support — Atlas">
  <main class="legal">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Support</h1>
      <p class="updated">We're here to help.</p>

      <h2>Contact us</h2>
      <p>
        For any question, bug report, or feedback, email
        <a href="mailto:aris@myatlas.fit">aris@myatlas.fit</a>. We aim to reply
        within one business day.
      </p>

      <h2>Common questions</h2>
      <h3>I can't sign in</h3>
      <p>
        Atlas uses email verification on first sign-in. Check your inbox (and
        spam folder) for a code from <strong>noreply@myatlas.fit</strong>. If
        the code doesn't arrive within a few minutes, email
        <a href="mailto:aris@myatlas.fit">aris@myatlas.fit</a> with the email
        address you tried.
      </p>

      <h3>How do I join my gym?</h3>
      <p>
        Your gym, trainer, or studio will send you an invitation by email or
        share a gym code. After you create an account, enter the code or follow
        the invitation link to join.
      </p>

      <h3>Can I use Atlas without a gym?</h3>
      <p>
        Yes. The base workout tracker is free for everyone. Choose
        <em>Continue as solo</em> when prompted for a gym code.
      </p>

      <h3>How do I delete my account?</h3>
      <p>
        Email <a href="mailto:aris@myatlas.fit">aris@myatlas.fit</a> from the
        address registered on your account and we'll delete your data within
        seven days. You can also delete your account in-app from
        <em>Settings &rarr; Delete account</em>.
      </p>

      <a href="/" class="back-link">Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding: 80px 0;
    min-height: 60vh;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--navy-700);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy-700);
    margin-top: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy-700);
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .updated {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--light-text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--light-text-secondary);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  a { color: var(--coral-600); }
  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
